observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor direct:
The Municipal Treasurer to enforce the collection of the underpayment of business taxes, including penalties and surcharges from these suppliers/contractors;
The Municipal Accountant to submit to the BPLO the names of the suppliers/contractors who transacted business with the Municipality including the payments made to them in the preceding calendar year to serve as basis for the computation of business taxes;
The Focal Person-BPLO to require the business taxpayers to submit Sworn Statements of all their gross sales/receipts (not only from the Municipality of Amadeo) for the preceding calendar year and other pertinent records/information for determination of gross receipts.
